id: pm-hfny
title: Pin GitHub Actions to immutable SHAs
description: "Harden CI, nightly, and release workflows by replacing mutable action version tags with the current immutable tag commit SHAs while preserving Dependabot tracking comments."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: ci,github-actions,pm-cli,security
created_at: "2026-05-03T13:57:09.345Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-03T14:03:20.014Z"
author: codex-audit
acceptance_criteria: "CI, nightly, and release workflows pin third-party and GitHub actions by full commit SHA with version comments; workflow contract tests assert the pinned references; targeted workflow tests pass."
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Pinned GitHub Actions workflow dependencies to immutable full commit SHAs while preserving version comments for maintainability.
expected_result: "CI, nightly, and release workflows use immutable SHA-pinned action references and contract tests assert those references."
actual_result: "Updated CI, nightly, and release workflows plus ci-workflow-contract tests. Workflow-contract linked test passed, no mutable @vN action references remain, security scan and full coverage passed."
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-03T13:57:09.345Z",codex-audit,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm search pin GitHub Actions SHA workflows --limit 10 and pm list-open --tag ci --limit 20 found only closed CI hardening items plus the active audit feature; latest official GitHub Actions security guidance still recommends immutable full-length SHA pinning."
  "2026-05-03T14:02:54.152Z",codex-audit,"Evidence: pinned checkout, setup-node, upload-artifact, and pnpm/action-setup workflow uses to full tag SHAs with version comments; verified no remaining workflow uses match mutable @vN action references. Linked test pm test pm-hfny --run passed. Final node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 84 files/1178 tests with 100% statements/branches/functions/lines. pnpm security:scan and git diff --check passed."
